Craft your own cuddly companion with this DIY Mini Crochet Kit featuring an adorable rabbit design! Perfect for crafters of all skill levels, this kit includes everything you need to create a charming handmade rabbit. A fun and rewarding project to enjoy or gift!

Product Details

  • Includes 4 x coloured yarns, 1 x crochet hook, 1 x plastic needle, 1 x ring stitch marker, 1 x 15g fibrefill and 1 x instruction sheet
  • Dimensions/Size: 22cm (H) x 15.5cm (W) x 7cm (D)
  • Material:
    • Yarn and fibrefill: Polyester and cotton
    • Crochet: Plastic and metal
    • Needle and ring stitch marker: Plastic
    • Instruction sheet: Paper

Features

  • Rabbit design
  • Makes one crochet rabbit
  • For DIY (do it yourself) craft
  • Easy peasy yarn!
  • Mini size

Additional Information

  • Instruction Manual

Warning: Choking hazard. Small parts. Follow usage instructions carefully.
